PROJECT DESIGN SUMMARY

  Purpose

  End-to-end object detector for retail shelf product detection. Inspired by GroundingDINO/DETR, trained from scratch on a custom COCO-format dataset. No text/language grounding —
  pure visual detection only.

  ---
  Dataset

  - Path: data/raw/coco_dataset/train/ — single split used; train/val is done in code
  - Annotations: annotations.json (COCO format)
  - Images: images/img_NNNNN.jpg
  - Stats: 248 images, 22,731 annotations, 356 product categories
  - Category IDs are remapped to contiguous 0-indexed labels: cat_id_to_idx / idx_to_cat_id dicts on the dataset object

